text: József Varró (born 2 March 1944) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pest County
